A *wildcard* is a symbolic representation of a text pattern.

= Wildcard List =
* *: Everyobject of any size.
* ?: Any singular character.
* [chars]: Any belonging to such set.
* [!chars]: Opposite of [chars].
* [[:class:]]: Any belonging to the provided character class.

= Character classes =
* *[:digit:]*
* *[:alpha:]*: Only letters
* *[:alnum:]* Alphanumeric
* *[:lower:]*
* *[:upper:]*
